{"tid":2445804,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"呢d路口通常邊個優先？","createTime":"2021-03-14T02:35:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T08:24:52.000Z","uid":127695,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"0b87c8b0a2a89acb81629737f75b3df631298540","tid":2445804,"uid":127695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:35:55.000Z","msg":"去到冇咁繁忙路口<br />\n冇交通燈又冇牌<br />\n大家要讓右邊車行先？<br />\n係規定定共識？上網搵唔到<br />\n例子1:<br />\n荔景華瑤路荔景山路交界<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DeqP2FV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDeqP2FV.png&h=f67c6f17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n假設兩車到X位置時間一樣<br />\n黃車要讓藍車行先？<br />\n<br />\n例子2:<br />\n大圍富健街顯康街交界<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gAiibzo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgAiibzo.png&h=861e0034&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n邊個先？<br />\n<br />\n又或者大路雙白線，轉左入小路再一手u turn出返大路<br />\n俾人告雙白線掉頭 但架車已經完全入晒小路 <br />\n<br />\n大家仲有咩易中伏位講下？"},{"pid":"0985e76b81312f106b21b0d068b591662c9aee41","tid":2445804,"uid":16061,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:45:54.000Z","msg":"狹路相逢勇者勝"},{"pid":"d3e2cb8bc942fcbf6b3cffc6dda1295bbcf05a95","tid":2445804,"uid":127695,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0985e76b81312f106b21b0d068b591662c9aee41","tid":2445804,"uid":16061,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T02:45:54.000Z","msg":"狹路相逢勇者勝"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T03:06:13.000Z","msg":"都唔係話勇既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係要避免意外發生 有時知多少少嘢對自己有着數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab57498f1ea2d6209b6879fc183d0c243d47e0f","tid":2445804,"uid":199227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T03:13:52.000Z","msg":"黃色優先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ff4b61fe872ffba54eb645d480146c8640bd05","tid":2445804,"uid":25260,"like":12,"dislike":